 operations team as the company scales You have 1.5+ years experience in a customer-facing position Superior written communications - writing samples Ability to explain technical processes to non-technical clients Experience building and maintaining procedural and FAQ content We Love People That Have A(n) Passion for making customer happy spark joy Interest in DEFI, cryptocurrencies and investing Have ideas to improve Customer Success Our Environment We love what we do! We\u2019re building something special that can transform banking and money forever Entrepreneurial and unstructured Supportive, empathic, and kind teammates Fast-moving, dynamic, and challenging International work environment Infinite career growth opportunities Flexible working hours, casual work attire Competitive Salary (with potential stock options) Please answer the 3 questions in the prompt on this page OR submit a short 1 paragraph cover letter. We read each one carefully. Unfortunately because of the high volume of applications, we will only consider applicants that have answered the prompt or submit a cover letter. Powered by JazzHR ", 
